JACKPOTS_DESCRIPTION_1:
Time jackpot is triggered randomly after the player has made a bet and must be won by a specific time.
Сloser to the end of the countdown timer, the chances of winning increase.
JACKPOTS_DESCRIPTION_2: Classic Jackpot is triggered randomly and can be won by any player.
JACKPOTS_DESCRIPTION_3:
Must Drop Jackpot is triggered randomly after the player has made a bet and is guaranteed to pay before reaching the maximum amount.
The chances of winning increase as the counter gets closer to the maximum amount.
JACKPOTS_RULES_1: Any player has a chance to win the **#JACKPOTS_NAME**!
JACKPOTS_RULES_10: Each bet contributes a small share to the Jackpot pool and is allocated between all types of **#JACKPOTS_NAME**.
JACKPOTS_RULES_11: Bet contribution is split into 2 pots: one part of bet contribution is gradually increasing the current **#JACKPOTS_NAME**, and the other part is used to accumulate the seed value of the next **#JACKPOTS_NAME**.
JACKPOTS_RULES_12: The Jackpot counter is reset to the Jackpot seed value, when one type of **#JACKPOTS_NAME** is won.
JACKPOTS_RULES_13: No symbol combinations resulting after player's spin affects the winning of **#JACKPOTS_NAME**. Spinning the reels for real money is the only way to randomly trigger the **#JACKPOTS_NAME**!
JACKPOTS_RULES_14: **#JACKPOTS_NAME** wins always come in the player's account currency.
JACKPOTS_RULES_15: If the player's currency is different from the **#JACKPOTS_NAME** currency, the winnings are paid in the player's currency in accordance with the exchange rate.
JACKPOTS_RULES_16: The daily updated exchange rate is based on an external independent source and corresponds to the one set on the **#JACKPOTS_NAME** server.
JACKPOTS_RULES_17: All players participating in **#JACKPOTS_NAME** will receive a notification when the **#JACKPOTS_NAME** is won by any other player.
JACKPOTS_RULES_18: The **#JACKPOTS_NAME** can be won only during the main game.
JACKPOTS_RULES_19: The **#JACKPOTS_NAME** is not available in demo mode.
JACKPOTS_RULES_20: The same **#JACKPOTS_NAME** cannot be claimed by two or more players at the same time.
JACKPOTS_RULES_21: Internet connection issues can lead to delays in notifications or updates of **#JACKPOTS_NAME** counters, but they do not affect the **#JACKPOTS_NAME** actual winnings.
JACKPOTS_RULES_22: Malfunction voids all pays and plays.
JACKPOTS_RULES_4: All bets made with real money take part in the **#JACKPOTS_NAME** drawing.
JACKPOTS_RULES_5: **#JACKPOTS_NAME** are a separate promotional tool working independently of a game's features.
JACKPOTS_RULES_6: There are 3 types of **#JACKPOTS_NAME**: Time, Classic (mini, minor, major and grand) and Must Drop. Each of them is presented with an individual title and position on the Jackpot widget panel when activated in a game.
JACKPOTS_RULES_7: **Time Jackpot** is triggered randomly after the player has made a bet and must be won by a specific time. **Time Jackpot** has a time limit and the closer the countdown is to running out of time, the higher the chances of winning the **Time Jackpot**. The winnings are guaranteed to be paid before **Time Jackpot** countdown timer runs out. In case the countdown timer runs out, the Jackpot will be triggered with the next bet placed on the server.
JACKPOTS_RULES_8: The **Must Drop Jackpot** is triggered randomly after a player has made a bet and is guaranteed to pay before reaching the maximum amount shown by the counter. The chance of winning the **Must Drop Jackpot** increases when the **Must Drop Jackpot** counter gets closer to the maximum amount. In case the Must Drop counter reaches the end, the Jackpot will be triggered with the next bet placed on the server.
JACKPOTS_RULES_9: The **Classic Jackpot** is triggered randomly and can be won by any player.
